IB/hfi1: Refactor get_user() IOCTLs

The IOCTL is a bit unwieldy.  Refactor to a common pattern.
Refactor _RECV_CTRL, _POLL_TYPE, _ACK_EVENT and _SET_PKEY
IOCTLs to a common pattern.

